0:00:00.060,0:00:02.000
My name is Geoffrey Okwengu.

0:00:02.000,0:00:04.420
I came all the way from Kenya.

0:00:04.420,0:00:07.220
The first time I came,

0:00:07.220,0:00:11.620
the problem that brought me here was HIV 1 and 2.

0:00:11.620,0:00:15.140
For how many years were you having this problem of HIV?

0:00:15.140,0:00:17.860
I had suffered for two years.

0:00:17.860,0:00:23.800
I discovered I was HIV positive when I was about to get married.

0:00:23.800,0:00:30.060
That is how the plans for marriage disappeared.

0:00:30.060,0:00:32.340
I was always getting sick.

0:00:32.340,0:00:38.240
That was why I decided to come to The SCOAN to be prayed for so that I would be healed.

0:00:38.240,0:00:42.120
Before you came, when you discovered that you were positive to HIV,

0:00:42.120,0:00:44.200
how did you feel?

0:00:44.200,0:00:49.180
I felt very sad and bad because I knew the enemy had me.

0:00:49.180,0:00:54.320
I was destined for the grave at a very early age.

0:00:54.320,0:00:57.440
I tested positive at Nairobi Hospital.

0:00:57.440,0:01:02.200
So I came here and the man of God prayed for me.

0:01:02.200,0:01:05.800
I was given the Morning Water and I went home.

0:01:05.800,0:01:08.580
I kept administering it.

0:01:08.580,0:01:12.200
After a while, I had a dream.

0:01:12.200,0:01:17.120
I had an encounter with the man of God, Prophet T.B. Joshua, in a dream

0:01:17.120,0:01:20.620
where he appeared to me.

0:01:20.620,0:01:26.400
It was in a theatre; he was operating on me.

0:01:26.400,0:01:31.680
After he had finished, he told me, "You are healed".

0:01:31.680,0:01:35.340
In the dream I said, "Thank You, Jesus. I'm healed".

0:01:35.340,0:01:39.200
Then I woke up from the dream.

0:01:39.200,0:01:45.480
Immediately after that, I found out that I was now getting better.

0:01:45.480,0:01:47.980
I was feeling okay; I was feeling good.

0:01:47.980,0:01:49.800
Then I went for a test.

0:01:49.800,0:01:52.980
I then discovered that I was HIV negative.

0:01:52.980,0:01:58.160
Shall we put our hands together for our Lord Jesus!

0:01:58.160,0:02:02.760
This is somebody who was given a certificate of death,

0:02:02.760,0:02:06.800
meaning someone who was tested HIV 1 and 2.

0:02:06.800,0:02:09.800
The man of God prayed for him in the midst of the crowd.

0:02:09.800,0:02:14.960
Can you tell us the name of the hospital that tested you right now negative.

0:02:14.960,0:02:16.360
It was Nairobi Hospital.

0:02:16.360,0:02:17.280
The same hospital?

0:02:17.280,0:02:18.160
Yes.

0:02:18.160,0:02:19.920
That once tested you positive?

0:02:19.920,0:02:20.580
Yes.

0:02:20.580,0:02:22.620
And you went back and now you are negative?

0:02:22.620,0:02:23.280
Yes.

0:02:23.280,0:02:26.820
Wow. Can you tell us - what happened after the man of God prayed for you?

0:02:26.820,0:02:28.500
I am totally free.

0:02:28.500,0:02:30.960
I was able to get married.

0:02:30.960,0:02:37.780
My marriage got delayed. Even my younger siblings - I'm the first born - got married before me.

0:02:37.780,0:02:42.360
I now got married; I had a very big wedding in 2013.

0:02:42.360,0:02:44.920
Now I have two boys.

0:02:44.920,0:02:49.540
Mr Geoffrey Okwengu
Morning Water Testimony

